# Dev

Dev is a set of utilities for rapid software development. It is opinionated software,
and as such uses tools that may not be a good fit for everyone.

## Commands

dev up - Spin up a dev session in RAMDISK.
dev down - Sync and tear down the RAMDISK session.

~
  .bashrc

    /x/d/support/dev
      + ruby/
      + spec/
      .rspec
      .ruby-gemset
      .ruby-version
      dev
      dev.xiki
      Gemfile
      Gemfile.lock

